







       An OptionButton should be used to post an Option Menu.

       This component must be composed of a button, with either a
       text or graphics label.  Following the label, this component
       should also include a bar graphic to distinguish it from a
       PushButton.  The label must be the last selection made from
       the OptionButton.





       An OptionButton must have no internal navigation.  The fol-
       lowing text describes the operations of this component.

